ReturnPolicy.Description:
For Returns - We offer an unconditional, no questions asked 100% money back policy for a maximum period of 30 Days, starting from the day you have received the item. If you find the product damaged or not as described on the listing, we are happy to refund your payment once we received the item.

Shipping charges are not refundable. Buyers pay the return shipping.

 The item must meet the following criteria to be eligible for a return:

1) Item must be in its original unworn condition

2) Item must not have been sized or customized in any way.

3) Item must be returned with all original accessories included with the purchase.

4) Buyer must contact us for a return form prior to shipping product back.

Please send us a message through ebay messages requesting a return form, and you will be sent one directly to your email address within 24 hours.

About Us Pretty Jewellery Pvt. Ltd. is a leading manufacturer and exporter of Gold and Silver Diamond Jewellery in Mumbai, India which has been founded in the year 2000. Pretty Jewellery Pvt. Ltd. has extensive experience in the diamond Jewellery industry since 1976. Our parent company M/S. S.R. Diamond for whom we are a Jewellery manufacturing unit has carved a niche for themselves by pioneering exports of loose diamonds and exotic Jewellery across the world We at Pretty Jewellery Pvt. Ltd. benchmark ourselves to be leaders in the Manufacturing and Export of Diamond Studded Jewellery from Mumbai across the globe. We have a dedicated team of over 125 craftsmen whose perseverance and hard-work maintains the quality required for silver and gold studded jewelry by our customers. We turnaround 1, 00,000 pcs annually. Though a mid-size company we have state of art machinery to match the customer’s quality requirement. We prepare product on orders basis and delivery is on time. We have a considerable sample line having array of product categories like rings, pendants, earrings and sets as per the international quality standards... Our jewellery designs are conceptualized and created keeping in mind international standards and trends. The unique and exotic jewellery patterns are crafted by our in house designers and artisans with utmost care and caution. Our production unit is prompt to delivery large orders due to our strong supply chain modeled on global delivery measures. Besides our extensive range of Catalogue Designs We also satisfy our customers with made to order designs to suit occasions and styles. Our manufacturing ranges in 9k to 18k Gold Jewellery based on choice and size of diamonds chosen by our esteemed clientele. Our exotic gold and silver diamond jewellery is exported to countries like USA, UK, Australia, Middle East, Far East, Europe to name a few.
